rogress speed throttles I\/O speed and makes progress bar flicker too much, setting it too high makes progress bar unresponsive. Current behaviour IMHO undermines usefulness of ProgressBar.\r\n\r\nThis is an attempt to replace this with more consistent experience, not requiring to know speed of progress. In Symfony 5 I expect to set this to sane default, so all users will get consistent redraw experience out of the box no matter the progress speed, but still leaving it configurable when e.g. somebody needs to run it on slow terminal. (does the last part make sense?)\r\n\r\nIf you want more tests, which I guess you do, please advise where and how to write them in a way they will be reliable, as they are gonna be time based.","created_at":"2018-02-28T01:21:24Z","updated_at":"2018-03-09T14:30:12Z","closed_at":null,"merged_at":null,"merge_commit_sha":"eecdc79df76ee3b38a194ae703cf1554197a33de","assignee":null,"assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[{"id":125388,"url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/symfony\/symfony\/labels\/Console","name":"Console","color":"DDDDDD","default":false},{"id":337186922,"url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/symfony\/symfony\/labels\/Deprecation","name":"Deprecation","color":"f1c40f","default":false},{"id":100378,"url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/symfony\/symfony\/labels\/Feature","name":"Feature","color":"02e10c","default":false},{"id":237003792,"url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/symfony\/symfony\/labels\/Status:%20Needs%20Review","name":"Status: Needs Review","color":"ededed","default":false}],"milestone":{"url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/symfony\/symfony\/milestones\/17","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/symfony\/symfony\/milestone\/17","labels_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/symfony\/symfony\/milestones\/17\/labels","id":2795131,"number":17,"title":"4.1","description":"https:\/\/symfony.com\/roadmap?version=4.1#checker","creator":{"login":"nicolas-grekas","id":243674,"avatar_url":